                <expan><ex>H</ex><abbr>oneratus</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/>et Lucia <lb n="3"/>qum <note>sic</note> filis <lb n="4"/>suis votum <lb n="5"/>quot <note>sic</note> fecerunt <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Weihung an die aures aus Dekor erschlossen (Ohrenpaar, in der Mitte Palme). (C): Benseddik denkt an Weihung an Fruchtbarkeitsgöttin Tanit - Caelestis (Ohren = Symbol für Erhörung).</p>
            </div>
